All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Hotel
Class that is the main entity used to store lists of different type of rooms.
HotelBuilder
Class that provides methods that create Hotel class and populate the lists of rooms.
Main  
MenuFunctions
Utility class that provides methods to perform operations on rooms in the hotel during user session.
OneBedroom
Class that extends Room abstract class and adds fields that are specific to this type of room.
Penthouse
Class that extends Room abstract class and adds fields that are specific to this type of room.
Room
Abstract class that contains the most relevant information that all child classes use.
Standard
Class that extends Room abstract class and adds fields that are specific to this type of room.
User
Class used in UserInterface class stores basic information about the person using hotel's menu and a list of rooms booked in current session.
UserInterface
Class used to display the hotel menu with different options that user may choose regarding rooms.
Users
Utility class to store all the User objects and return an object of User class during logging in to UserInterface.
